@startuml 04-instagram-redirect
!theme plain
title Shortcuts redirect: native Instagram → ScrollGuard Clone

actor User
participant "OnboardingView" as Onboarding
participant "iOS Shortcuts\nautomation" as Shortcuts
participant "Instagram\n(native app)" as NativeIG
participant "ScrollGuardCloneApp" as App
participant "ContentView" as CV

== One-time setup ==
User -> Onboarding : open walkthrough\n(first launch, or from Settings)
Onboarding -> Shortcuts : openURL("shortcuts://")
User -> Shortcuts : create automation —\n"When Instagram Is Opened\n→ Run Immediately\n→ Open App: ScrollGuard Clone"
User -> Onboarding : tap "It works — I'm done"
Onboarding -> Onboarding : sg.redirectSetupDone = true\n(UserDefaults)

== Every day after ==
User -> NativeIG : tap the Instagram icon
NativeIG -> Shortcuts : "Instagram Is Opened"\ntrigger fires
Shortcuts -> App : Open App action\nforegrounds ScrollGuard Clone
App -> CV : onAppear\n(redirectSetupDone == true,\nonboarding sheet skipped)
CV -> User : filtered WKWebView\n(session persisted from before)

note right of NativeIG
  Instagram flashes briefly, then the
  automation bounces the user straight
  into the filtered client instead.
end note
@enduml
